#: ../../src/user/nodes-system/managing-nodes.rst:6
msgid "Nodes are the most important part of Roadiz CMS. They are your content which can be shaped as you want according to your node-types definitions. A node can be a blog-post, a content page, a photo gallery, even a shop product. This is why we called it “Node”, it’s an abstract data container interconnected with other node in a tree."
msgstr ""

